99b5987f462c1a7bc4eb61ae2f7f2527cf196","tid":2274063,"uid":85708,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T00:03:05.000Z","msg":"而家d 人講真相就俾人話係fake news<br />\n跟住d 媒體講話無d 咁ge 事<br />\n好似tvb 咁 <br />\n講真相但無人信 變左你講大話咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:14:36.000Z","msg":"左膠表示冇左霉fact check 所以係假嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:19:23.000Z","msg":"左謀查：fact check <br />\n法庭查：輸打贏要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae50a561f34f728a5fa43c9ab27c71ecec54380","tid":2274063,"uid":149531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b3699b5987f462c1a7bc4eb61ae2f7f2527cf196","tid":2274063,"uid":85708,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T00:03:05.000Z","msg":"而家d 人講真相就俾人話係fake news<br />\n跟住d 媒體講話無d 咁ge 事<br />\n好似tvb 咁 <br />\n講真相但無人信 變左你講大話咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打走先，我幫你頂住呢度"},{"pid":"d20781691493e006c44caf299f2bf24da0c7186f","tid":2274063,"uid":379900,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:27:54.000Z","msg":"另一個post度貼完全冇人理<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Benford%27s_law#Election_data\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FBenford%2527s_law%23Election_data&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9sorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=680106f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Benford%27s_law#Election_data</a><br />\nBenford's law has been invoked as evidence of fraud in the 2009 Iranian elections,[34] and also used to analyze other election results. <span class=\"red\">However, other experts consider Benford's law problematical or misleading as a statistical indicator of election fraud.[35]</span><br />\n<br />\n[35]篇paper<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cambridge.org/core/services/aop-cambridge-core/content/view/3B1D64E822371C461AF3C61CE91AAF6D/S1047198700012808a.pdf/benfords_law_and_the_detection_of_election_fraud.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fservices%2Faop-cambridge-core%2Fcontent%2Fview%2F3B1D64E822371C461AF3C61CE91AAF6D%2FS1047198700012808a.pdf%2Fbenfords_law_and_the_detection_of_election_fraud.pdf&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9sorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=460219d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cambridge.org/core/services/aop-cambridge-core/content/view/3B1D64E822371C461AF3C61CE91AAF6D/S1047198700012808a.pdf/benfords_law_and_the_detection_of_election_fraud.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nAbstract:<br />\nThe proliferation of elections in even those states that are arguably anything but democratic has given rise to a focused interest on developing methods for detecting fraud in the official statistics of a state&rsquo;s election returns. Among these efforts are those that employ Benford&rsquo;s Law, with the most common application being an attempt to proclaim some election or another fraud free or replete with fraud. This essay, however, argues that, despite its apparent utility in looking at other phenomena, Benford&rsquo;s Law is problematical at best as a forensic tool when applied to elections. Looking at simulations designed to model both fair and fraudulent contests as well as data drawn from elections we know, on the basis of other investigations, were either permeated by fraud or unlikely to have experienced any measurable malfeasance, we find that conformity with and deviations from Benford&rsquo;s Law follow no pattern. It is not simply that the Law occasionally judges a fraudulent election fair or a fair election fraudulent. <span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">Its &lsquo;&lsquo;success rate&rsquo;&rsquo; either way is essentially equivalent to a toss of a coin, thereby rendering it problematical at best as a forensic tool and wholly misleading at worst.</span></span><br />\n<br />\n連登仔可唔可以搵一篇paper係用數學證明係一個合理election model之下<br />\nd data係應該乎合Benford's law?"},{"pid":"6895d5d997f40a1d5badcae275e550c2d53c04b5","tid":2274063,"uid":121784,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:45:59.000Z","msg":"作為對大數據有興趣既人，我對呢個現象好有興趣。<br />\n<br />\n唔知邊度可以拎到各候選人，係每個郡既得票，要純文字，方便電腦處理，唔要各大網站見到既靚靚地圖。我想研究一下。<br />\n<br />\n暫時睇到既解釋：<a href=\"https://www.eipartnership.net/rapid-response/what-the-election-results-dont-tell-us?src=ilaw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eipartnership.net%2Frapid-response%2Fwhat-the-election-results-dont-tell-us%3Fsrc%3Dilaw&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9sorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=799c92a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eipartnership.net/rapid-response/what-the-election-results-dont-tell-us?src=ilaw</a>"},{"pid":"9aefb00888b6ba43cf2f7b6950efc94aec2bb742","tid":2274063,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3699b5987f462c1a7bc4eb61ae2f7f2527cf196","tid":2274063,"uid":85708,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T00:03:05.000Z","msg":"而家d 人講真相就俾人話係fake news<br />\n跟住d 媒體講話無d 咁ge 事<br />\n好似tvb 咁 <br />\n講真相但無人信 變左你講大話咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:57:03.000Z","msg":"Basless claim... 跟住話你misinformation<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431e21a2251882a9ceccc90077fb85f72b965195","tid":2274063,"uid":73095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6895d5d997f40a1d5badcae275e550c2d53c04b5","tid":2274063,"uid":121784,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:45:59.000Z","msg":"作為對大數據有興趣既人，我對呢個現象好有興趣。<br />\n<br />\n唔知邊度可以拎到各候選人，係每個郡既得票，要純文字，方便電腦處理，唔要各大網站見到既靚靚地圖。我想研究一下。<br />\n<br />\n暫時睇到既解釋：<a href=\"https://www.eipartnership.net/rapid-response/what-the-election-results-dont-tell-us?src=ilaw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.