2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9sorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=680106f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Benford%27s_law#Election_data</a><br />\nBenford's law has been invoked as evidence of fraud in the 2009 Iranian elections,[34] and also used to analyze other election results. <span class=\"red\">However, other experts consider Benford's law problematical or misleading as a statistical indicator of election fraud.[35]</span><br />\n<br />\n[35]篇paper<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cambridge.org/core/services/aop-cambridge-core/content/view/3B1D64E822371C461AF3C61CE91AAF6D/S1047198700012808a.pdf/benfords_law_and_the_detection_of_election_fraud.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fservices%2Faop-cambridge-core%2Fcontent%2Fview%2F3B1D64E822371C461AF3C61CE91AAF6D%2FS1047198700012808a.pdf%2Fbenfords_law_and_the_detection_of_election_fraud.pdf&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9sorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=460219d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cambridge.org/core/services/aop-cambridge-core/content/view/3B1D64E822371C461AF3C61CE91AAF6D/S1047198700012808a.pdf/benfords_law_and_the_detection_of_election_fraud.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nAbstract:<br />\nThe proliferation of elections in even those states that are arguably anything but democratic has given rise to a focused interest on developing methods for detecting fraud in the official statistics of a state&rsquo;s election returns. Among these efforts are those that employ Benford&rsquo;s Law, with the most common application being an attempt to proclaim some election or another fraud free or replete with fraud. This essay, however, argues that, despite its apparent utility in looking at other phenomena, Benford&rsquo;s Law is problematical at best as a forensic tool when applied to elections. Looking at simulations designed to model both fair and fraudulent contests as well as data drawn from elections we know, on the basis of other investigations, were either permeated by fraud or unlikely to have experienced any measurable malfeasance, we find that conformity with and deviations from Benford&rsquo;s Law follow no pattern. It is not simply that the Law occasionally judges a fraudulent election fair or a fair election fraudulent. <span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">Its &lsquo;&lsquo;success rate&rsquo;&rsquo; either way is essentially equivalent to a toss of a coin, thereby rendering it problematical at best as a forensic tool and wholly misleading at worst.</span></span><br />\n<br />\n連登仔可唔可以搵一篇paper係用數學證明係一個合理election model之下<br />\nd data係應該乎合Benford's law?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T11:24:50.000Z","msg":"清,我見無人覆你就覆下你啦<br />\n一search google scholar 已經見到有個University of Michigan (QS Ranking: 21) professor 寫文話你引用個篇文有問題<br />\n&quot;Comment on &ldquo;Benford's Law and the Detection of Election Fraud&rdquo;&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/political-analysis/article/comment-on-benfords-law-and-the-detection-of-election-fraud/BC29680D8B5469A54C7C9D865029FE7C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fjournals%2Fpolitical-analysis%2Farticle%2Fcomment-on-benfords-law-and-the-detection-of-election-fraud%2FBC29680D8B5469A54C7C9D865029FE7C&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9sorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=ba9f893b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/political-analysis/article/comment-on-benfords-law-and-the-detection-of-election-fraud/BC29680D8B5469A54C7C9D865029FE7C</a><br />\nBTW不如睇下D國際學術期刊啦,佢地D比較持平D<br />\nPublished By: Institute of Mathematical Statistics<br />\n<a href=\"https://projecteuclid.org/download/pdfview_1/euclid.ss/1330437932\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprojecteuclid.org%2Fdownload%2Fpdfview_1%2Feuclid.ss%2F1330437932&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9sorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=2cf8adf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://projecteuclid.org/download/pdfview_1/euclid.ss/1330437932</a><br />\n同埋我想講, 而家唔只Benford's law 話佢有可能有fraud, 其實仲有好多助證見到個選舉係有問題<br />\n唔比人監票, 一邊點票一邊收票，D票係同一個城市可以寄左3日先&quot;續批續批&quot;到等等等"},{"pid":"935024600f912caf0540f6a488305cb5bc4593b2","tid":2274063,"uid":185990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"431e21a2251882a9ceccc90077fb85f72b965195","tid":2274063,"uid":73095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6895d5d997f40a1d5badcae275e550c2d53c04b5","tid":2274063,"uid":121784,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:45:59.000Z","msg":"作為對大數據有興趣既人，我對呢個現象好有興趣。<br />\n<br />\n唔知邊度可以拎到各候選人，係每個郡既得票，要純文字，方便電腦處理，唔要各大網站見到既靚靚地圖。我想研究一下。<br />\n<br />\n暫時睇到既解釋：<a href=\"https://www.eipartnership.net/rapid-response/what-the-election-results-dont-tell-us?src=ilaw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eipartnership.net%2Frapid-response%2Fwhat-the-election-results-dont-tell-us%3Fsrc%3Dilaw&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9sorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=799c92a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eipartnership.net/rapid-response/what-the-election-results-dont-tell-us?src=ilaw</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T05:35:47.000Z","msg":"有人解釋過<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/gelbach/status/1324761001280081921\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgelbach%2Fstatus%2F1324761001280081921&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9sorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=4121ad3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgelbach%2Fstatus%2F1324761001280081921&h=7c48c304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/gelbach/status/1324761001280081921</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T17:56:44.000Z","msg":"佢講得幾合理，大家好似冇諗過Benford&rsquo;s Law幾時先啱用，呢啲數據真係冇辦法證實到有假票"},{"pid":"5d15e07b480ade97165e9e878e6c7427579f85b8","tid":2274063,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T18:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets